{"about_the_game":"<strong>SISYPHE</strong> is an adventure game about a square that yearns to be a circle. Chip off pieces of the square at certain points along the journey, and climb a mountain in search of <strong>renewal</strong>. You'll walk and climb through <strong>seven</strong> visually distinct areas on your way up the mountain path. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/Gif3-ezgif.com-resize__2_.gif?t=1738535824\" /><br><br><strong>SISYPHE</strong> is an mainly an <strong>interactive art piece</strong>. It's a beautiful, casual climbing game that prioritizes <strong>atmosphere</strong> and the journey. SISYPHE keeps a unique visual style that embodies the feel and soul of the square's voyage. Listen to a beautiful soundtrack by <strong>Pierre Scheuer</strong> (PeterBarn) and creator <strong>Lucas Ljunggren</strong> along the way.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/Gif4-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1738535824\" /><br><br><strong>Explore a gorgeous world</strong> of climbing possibilites. <strong>No</strong> invisible walls, <strong>no</strong> restrictions, climb anywhere you can. Find large artifacts and statues along the way, a good place to take the atmosphere in and stare at the <strong>incredible</strong> landscapes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/Gif1-ezgif.com-resize__1_.gif?t=1738535824\" /><br><br>Explore <strong>SISYPHE</strong>, the beautiful, casual climbing game about the <strong>square</strong>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/Gif2-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1738535824\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738535824","background_raw":"https: